Hell, absolute hell.
Icefrog has damned all our souls to the darkest and sweatiest pits of hell;
Embrace it, feel the toxicity and the angry teenagers seeping with anger from every possible crevice;
Best dressing game i've ever played. 

Icefrog/10

client is not optimized as a proper 2022 game - lots of bugs and stutters that don't happen in any other game I play on my modern PC;

community is also hyper toxic and the game doesn't provide viable options for new players to get in

don't you even think about playing this game
